    <div class="metric"><b>$480K</b><br>HRSA grant</div>
    <div class="metric"><b>OVERDUE</b><br>report status</div>
    <div class="metric"><b>84%</b><br>Form 990</div>
    <div class="output">ASC 958 module tracks restricted funds, grant utilization, HRSA escalation, and Form 990 readiness.</div>
    <button onclick="location.href='/html/financial/index.html?v=asc958-demo'">OPEN FINANCIAL INTEL</button>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>3 · FINOPS MAIN STRATEGIST</h2>
    <p>Executive output layer: lanes, action log, business outcome, and $1,250/month close.</p>
    <div class="metric"><b>5 / 5</b><br>nodes reporting</div>
    <div class="metric"><b>12–18 hrs</b><br>saved monthly</div>
    <div class="metric"><b>$1,250/mo</b><br>system price</div>
    <div class="output" id="mainOut">Waiting for FinOps cycle output...</div>
    <button onclick="pushMain()">PUSH TO FINOPS MAIN</button>
    <button onclick="location.href='/html/finops-main-strategist/index.html?v=finops-demo'">OPEN FINOPS MAIN</button>
  </section>
</div>

<section class="close">
  <b>30-SECOND INTY CLOSE</b>
  <p>
  “Right here — these are your QuickBooks transactions, AP invoices, reconciliation work, and month-end support.
  The system flags issues before close, organizes the work immediately, and gives your controller an action-ready report.
  Most teams pay $5K–$7K/month for this manually. TSM delivers it as a visible operating system for $1,250/month.
  Would you rather start this alongside your current workflow, or replace part of it right away?”
  </p>
</section>

</main>

<div class="footer">
<span>● FINOPS PRESENTATION · FINANCIAL COMMAND + ASC 958 + MAIN STRATEGIST</span>
<span>READY</span>
</div>

<script>
function set(id,txt){document.getElementById(id).textContent=txt}

async function runCycle(){
  set('cmdOut',
`FINOPS CYCLE RUNNING

✓ Financial Intel: AP queue + AR risk analyzed
✓ Tax Intelligence: 1099 / W-9 readiness checked
✓ Compliance Shield: supporting docs reviewed
✓ Zero Trust: QuickBooks access risk checked
✓ Strategist: BNCA generated`);

  set('mainOut',
`SYSTEM RESULT:
→ 12 vendor invoices prioritized
→ 3 reconciliation issues flagged before month-end close
→ 7 vendors moved into 1099 readiness review
→ Controller report prepared

VALUE:
12–18 hours/month immediately saved.
$5K–$7K/month manual workload replaced by $1,250/month system.`);

  try{
    await fetch('/api/finops/report',{
      method:'POST',
      headers:{'content-type':'application/json'},
      body:JSON.stringify({
        title:'FinOps Presentation Cycle',
        summary:document.getElementById('mainOut').textContent,
        metrics:{apInvoices:12,reconItems:3,vendors1099:7,timeSaved:'12–18 hrs/month'}
      })
    });
  }catch(e){}
}

function pushMain(){
  localStorage.setItem('tsm_finops_report', JSON.stringify({
    ts:new Date().toISOString(),
    title:'FinOps Presentation Executive Output',
    summary:document.getElementById('mainOut').textContent || 'FinOps cycle pushed to Main Strategist.'
  }));
  location.href='/html/finops-main-strategist/index.html?v=from-finops-presentation';
}
</script>

<script id="tsm-finops-closing-system">
function showClose(){
  const old = document.getElementById("finopsExecutiveClose");
