      <div style="background:#061018;border:1px solid #123050;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px">
        <b style="color:#00e0ff">SYSTEM RESULT</b><br><br>
        → Bank reconciliation variance identified before close<br>
        → Vendor invoices prioritized by timing and support status<br>
        → 1099 / W-9 readiness surfaced before deadline risk<br>
