      <div style="background:#031a14;border:1px solid #00f59f;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px">
        <b style="color:#00f59f">ROI SNAPSHOT</b><br><br>
        Manual accounting coordination: <b>$6K–$10K/month</b><br>
        TSM Financial Operations Layer: <b>$1,750/month</b><br>
        Estimated time saved: <b>12–18 hours/month</b>
      </div>

      <div style="color:#00e0ff;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.5">
        This is not another dashboard — this is the accounting operations layer running in real time.
      </div>
